#!/bin/bash

sudo -v # ask for password only at the beginning

brew update
brew upgrade
brew tap homebrew/versions
brew tap phinze/homebrew-cask

brew install android-sdk ant autoconf automake brew-cask brew-rmtree cmake gcc gcc48 git gsl ios-sim lapack libgpg-error libksba libtool libxml2 libxslt libyaml llvm makedepend mysql node openssl phantomjs pkg-config postgresql python qt readline redis sqlite ssh-copy-id tcl-tk terminal-notifier wget

brew cask install android-studio appcleaner caffeine calibre cheatsheet chromium cyberduck disk-inventory-x firefox handbrake imageoptim iterm2 keycastr launchcontrol menumeters onyx pgadmin3 postgres skype sourcetree spectacle sqlite-database-browser the-unarchiver timemachineeditor tinkertool torbrowser transmission vienna vlc
